      <abstract obkms_id="abd06151-f11e-40a4-b7b5-762cdac6ee60" obkms_process="TRUE">
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>The generic name <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="887b4a9f-bc0f-4071-8bbf-6e8e7d64597a" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Dichodon</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> (Bartl. ex Rchb.) Rchb. was previously reinstated based on results from recent molecular phylogenetic studies. Accordingly, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="a1db4524-ba83-49b0-a446-70ca12bc4566" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Dichodon</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">parvipetalum</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> (Hosok.) G. Yao, a new combination for the species <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="95d71ec1-b55e-42d6-8a3a-e32f721d7e8e" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Cerastium</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">parvipetalum</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Hosok. is proposed.</p>
      </abstract>
